 step1
 
 when the user enter the username 
we add the player to the backend waiting room
we find other player that are available in the room
if there is any, we pair the players
create a pairPlayer relationship for the each player which 
contains the gameRoomId for the users

The players will listen to the pairPlayer table. This will allows the players to know who they are paired with.

Then they players can listen to the game played.